### HYMN CVI

#### A prayer for pardon of sin

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_0710601">1</span></span>Each
thoughtless ill that we have done, O Agni, all error in our  
   conduct, Jātavedas!  
  Therefrom do thou, O sapient God, preserve us. May we thy  
   friends, for bliss, have life eternal.

